LEGACY watched as TUCSON and TALON embrace and consider what will
happen in the future. "Taking her to her chambers would, in all
probability, be the best course of action."

BUMP nodded and smiled, "Yeah, it will be a while before she is going
to need the medical bay."

There was an answering smile from SANTON, "You take care of her
Tucson." He said. "I am going to help Leo." He also turned to leave
the room.

(TAG)

- Preston
